Record Point has x: i32; y: i32.

Union Event has none; click point: Point and button: u8.

To main, giving i32.
Let p be Point with x be 3 and y be 4.
Let event be Event.click with point be p and button be 2.
Give match event:
Event.click with point and button gives point.x plus point.y plus (button as i32);
otherwise gives 0.
